<h1 id="toc0"><span>来世之蛇 /// 天堂之上的基金会</span></h1>
<p><strong><a href="http://scpper.com/page/933265595">Stats</a> <span style="color: grey">|</span> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=m27ZTza7DUc">♪</a></strong></p>
</div>
<hr />
<p><strong>作者：</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nagiros" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4665703); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4665703&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1600571120" alt="Nagiros" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4665703)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nagiros" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4665703); return false;">Nagiros</a></span>，现在已经有了自己的<strong><a class="newpage" href="/nagiros">人事页</a></strong>.</p>
